Welcome to ZeroRotate's documentation!
======================================

**ZeroRotate** is an open-source PyTorch benchmark for performing scalable rotation detection on various datasets, which is maintained by `Yue Zhou <https://zytx121.github.io/>`_ and `Xue Yang <https://yangxue0827.github.io/>`_ with Shanghai Jiao Tong University supervised by Prof. `Jiang Xue <https://sp.sjtu.edu.cn/>`_.
